TITLE

  MFR - MagicFileRequester

VERSION

  2.0c - Minor update to 2.0

AUTHOR

  Stefan Stuntz (stuntz@informatik.tu-muenchen.de)

DESCRIPTION

  MFR is a replacement for all other file requesters.
  Features include complete keyboard control, nice outfit,
  proportional font support, directory caching, file find
  mechanism, file class support, file notification, many
  configuration options, history list, ...

NEW FEATURES

  Some changes from 2.0 are

  - Fixed division by zero guru with zero-size-file-systems (e.g. ParNet).
  - Fixed gadget activation bug.
  - Added menu item to rescan the device list.
  - reqtools.library patch can now be tested with the unregistered release.
  - Improved icon outfit on oldstyle screens.
  - Fixed file action bug.
  - Added semaphore security to string gadget handling.
  - Some code optimizations.
  - A4 is now saved for callback hooks.

  For detailed information, refer to the history file of the
  distribution archive.

